data.title: TV Schedule for FOX (WCHS-DT2) Charleston, WV
data.meta_description: Check out today's TV schedule for FOX (WCHS-DT2) Charleston, WV and take a look at what is scheduled for the next 2 weeks.
data.text:
Hot Bench Roaches, Cats & Rats, Oh My! New

A tenant accuses her former landlord of failing to exterminate pests, sending only his brother with a few sticky traps; furthermore, she says he kept her deposit in bad faith; he says his brother is a licensed exterminator, and he owes her nothing.

Karamo DNA: Who Do I Belong To?; Mom, You Pressure Me Too Much!

Keisha has been searching for her parents since she was 18 and believes that Curt could be her father; Bianca says she's provided her daughter, Nola, with everything to be successful, but Nola is closed off, apathetic and headed down the wrong path.

Maury My Wife Needs to Know ... I'm Sleeping With Her Best Friend!

Mohammad is from a country that encourages men to have multiple wives, and Kenyatta fears he has a secret family; Josh has a revelation that could have life-changing reverberations; Michelle thinks her boyfriend and her cousin are having an affair.

The Steve Wilkos Show Dad Went to Prison for Molesting Me: Did Mom Know?

Deonna, as a child, was sexually molested by her father for years, and she thinks her mother, Natasha, knew about the abuse but elected to ignore it.

Modern Family Won't You Be Our Neighbor

Phil and Claire panic when an obnoxious couple looks at the house for sale next door; Jay learns Manny's girlfriend is the granddaughter of a business rival -- after forbidding Manny to see her; Cam and Mitch are scared of Lily's teacher (Tyne Daly).

Two and a Half Men Zejdz Zmoich Wlosow (Get Off My Hair)

When Judith's pipes burst after an earthquake, Alan invites her to stay with him at Charlie's house.

Judge Judy Vegas Birthday Fail!; Puppy Takes a Bad Fall!; Rookie Driver Mistake!

Sisters fight over an unpaid loan and damages to a rental car; a dog's owner blames a baby sitter for its broken leg; a teen admits to hitting a fellow motorist when she had only two days of driving experience.
